<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ḥml ạllh yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā ḥamala ạllhi yasūʿ̊
 biạlrũwḥi naj̊tẖū biạl̊kẖusẖūʿ̊
 nan̊ẓuru ḥubã ạlậbi bal̊
 wamaj̊dahu ạlsãạmī ạlrãfīʿ̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ yas̊ṭaʿāni biạl̊bahā
 fī waj̊hika ạl̊ḥul̊wi ạl̊badīʿ̊

[V2]
 2- ḥiḍ̊nu ạảbīka yā ạb̊na ạllh̊
 kāna walam̊ yazal̊ suk̊nāk̊
 kun̊ta surūrahu wakun̊ta
 fariḥaⁿạ daẘmaⁿạ hunāk̊
 wakun̊ta maʿ̊hu wāḥidaⁿạ
 fī maj̊dika wafī bahāk̊

[V3]
 3- mutãḍiʿaⁿạ fī ạl̊midẖ̊wadi
 yā ḥamala ạllhi narāk̊
 narāka sāyỉḥaⁿạ gẖarīb̊
 fī ʿālamiⁿ ạảr̊sat̊ yadāk̊
 lạ mas̊nada litas̊tarīḥ̊
 ại̹n̊ biạlsẖãqā kẖārat̊ qūāk̊

[V4]
 4- wāi̹dẖ̊ narāka fid̊yaẗaⁿ
 yā rabãnā ạl̊fādī ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 ạủẘtẖiq̊ta kāldẖãbīḥaẗi
 ḥatãy̱ ại̹lay̱ ʿūdi ạlṣãlīb̊
 lituḍ̊raba ʿan̊ dẖan̊binā
 wataḥ̊mila ạl̊ḥuk̊ma ạlrãhīb̊

[V5]
 5- nah̊tifu min̊ ạảʿ̊māqinā
 ạảḥ̊bab̊tanā ḥatãy̱ ạldãmi
 maj̊daⁿạ laka maj̊daⁿạ laka
 biạl̊qal̊bi nasẖ̊dū wāl̊fami
 yā ḥamala ạllhi laka
 nasẖ̊dū biạảs̊may̱ nagẖami</lyrics>
</song>